🔹 C. YEAR-WISE METHOD (IMPORTANT)
🔹 Example 2

P = 1000
R = 10%
T = 2 years

Year 1:
Interest = 100
New amount = 1100

Year 2:
Interest = 110
Final amount = 1210

CI = 210

